[Another version of this report also attributed to UNICEF cites the number of casualties as 34. Another account of this incident involved poliovirus vaccine in addition to measles vaccine and can be read in the ProMED-mail posts: Vaccine adverse event - Syria (ID, DY): muscle relaxant, fatalities 20140918.2784470 and Vaccine adverse event, fatalities - Syria (02): (ID, DY) muscle relaxant 20140920.2790839.

Idlib governorate, which is the site of this incident, is held by moderate rebel groups opposed to both Syria's dictator, Bashar al-Assad, and the extremist Islamic State in Iraq and Syria (ISIS), according to the UNICEF report. - Mod.CP

